        "children": [],
        "sourceLabel": "Nos valeurs",
        "category": "about",
        "rawHtml": "<section class=\"bg-[var(--bg)] p-[80px_40px]\"><div class=\"text-center mb-[52px]\"><span class=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-[var(--brand)] tracking-[.13em] uppercase block mb-[12px]\">Nos valeurs</span><h2 class=\"text-[2rem] font-black text-[var(--text)] tracking-[-.025em] leading-[1.1]\">Ce qui nous guide</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-[20px]\"><div class=\"bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--line)] rounded-[18px] p-[28px] text-center\"><div class=\"w-[48px] h-[48px] rounded-[14px] bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand)_12%,transparent)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-[16px] text-[var(--brand)] text-[18px] font-black\">01</div><h3 class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-[8px]\">Innovation</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[var(--muted)] leading-[1.65]\">Toujours a la pointe pour vous offrir le meilleur.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--line)] rounded-[18px] p-[28px] text-center\"><div class=\"w-[48px] h-[48px] rounded-[14px] bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand)_12%,transparent)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-[16px] text-[var(--brand)] text-[18px] font-black\">02</div><h3 class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-[8px]\">Transparence</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[var(--muted)] leading-[1.65]\">Communication claire et honnete en toutes circonstances.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--line)] rounded-[18px] p-[28px] text-center\"><div class=\"w-[48px] h-[48px] rounded-[14px] bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand)_12%,transparent)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-[16px] text-[var(--brand)] text-[18px] font-black\">03</div><h3 class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-[8px]\">Excellence</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[var(--muted)] leading-[1.65]\">La qualite au coeur de chaque decision.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[var(--surface)] border border-[var(--line)] rounded-[18px] p-[28px] text-center\"><div class=\"w-[48px] h-[48px] rounded-[14px] bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand)_12%,transparent)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-[16px] text-[var(--brand)] text-[18px] font-black\">04</div><h3 class=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-[var(--text)] mb-[8px]\">Proximite</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[var(--muted)] leading-[1.65]\">Un accompagnement humain et personnalise.</p></div></div></section>"
